@startuml
title Start / Complete Examination - Sequence Design
autonumber
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Veterinarian" as Vet
participant "Web SPA" as Web
participant "api-gateway" as Gateway
participant "visits-service\nVisitController" as Visits
participant "VisitService" as Service
database "visits schema" as DB
queue "RabbitMQ" as MQ

Vet -> Web: Open assigned visit
Web -> Gateway: PATCH /api/v1/visits/{id}/start
Gateway -> Visits: route with VET JWT
Visits -> Service: startVisit(id, vetId)
Service -> DB: transition SCHEDULED -> IN_PROGRESS
Visits --> Web: VisitResponse

Vet -> Web: Enter diagnosis, treatment, fee
Web -> Gateway: PATCH /api/v1/visits/{id}/complete
Gateway -> Visits: route
Visits -> Service: completeVisit(id, request)
Service -> DB: transition IN_PROGRESS -> COMPLETED
Service -> MQ: publish VisitCompletedEvent
Visits --> Web: completed VisitResponse
@enduml
